summary:
Happy (belated) New Year everyone! 

I hope 2019 is treating everyone well so far! 

I've been messing with some new Arteza...
caption:
Happy (belated) New Year everyone!

I hope 2019 is treating everyone well so far!

I’ve been messing with some new Arteza brush tip water color markers! I’m not super happy with how this came out, I’m too impatient to wait for the ink to dry and that led to the ink bleeding, and uhg. But hey, lessons were learned. :P

All the same though, it was fun and it’s still kinda cute. XD I went back with some other pens to clean it up, and I may eventually touch it up digitally.

The brushes themselves are lovely. The tips are bristled and the ink is easily workable. I had problems with it feathering, although i think that may have more to do with me not being used to watercolors rarher than the pens themselves. I am however a little upset that one of my brown pens ran out of ink almost immeadiately. The rest seem to be doing okay, and a 24 pack was only $22, so not bad at all for the price.

#aggretsuko #retsuko #haida #fanartfriday #fanart #metal #anime #netflix #happynewyear #NAUTIART #nauti #art #arteza #illustrations

summary: Wow that Aggretsuko movie was... really really bad. Like I feel like it ruined a lot of the show for me bad. First off we find...
body: Wow that Aggretsuko movie was… really really bad. Like I feel like it ruined a lot of the show for me bad. First off we find out she rejected Haida so the plot of them trying to awkwardly/cutely plan a Christmas date like I thought this would be is right out the window. Instead we have a plot about Retsuko trying to take a good instagram picture for Christmas. That’s it. She has to make last minute plans to get a good picture because if she doesn’t apparently her instagram followers will be disappointed. I have never in my entire life heard a more boring idea for a 22 minute fucking “movie” I actually want to beat the viewing out of my brain. It scrapped tons of interesting stuff the finale of the show set up and didn’t give any interesting characters anything to do for a fucking SELFIE PLOT. THERE WASN’T EVEN ANY DEATH METAL OR AGGRESSIVE SCREAMING, WHO APPROVED THIS? All you had to do was have Haida and Aggretsuko be dating but too nervous to ask each other on a Christmas date for like 10 minutes, then the last half would be them going around having fun and end it with karaoke death metal, how hard would that be? Jesus ever loving Christ how do you fuck up this bad

gori and washimi are such bad bitches and i support the mentor-like role they’ve assumed
